---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About | HealthAI Notes"
	description="About HealthAI Notes and the editorial focus on practical AI in healthcare."
>
	<main class="page">
		<section class="page-section">
			<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
			<h1>Why this site exists.</h1>
			<p class="lede">
				HealthAI Notes is a small publishing project for people who want a cleaner read on where
				AI helps healthcare operations and where it mostly creates noise.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="two-up">
			<article class="page-section">
				<p class="kicker">Editorial Focus</p>
				<h2>Practical, not promotional</h2>
				<p class="muted">
					The intent is to write in plain language about workflow, documentation, model
					evaluation, governance, and implementation tradeoffs.
				</p>
			</article>
			<article class="page-section">
				<p class="kicker">Audience</p>
				<h2>Built for operators and clinicians</h2>
				<p class="muted">
					Useful for founders, clinicians, informatics teams, and anyone trying to separate real
					process improvement from polished demos.
				</p>
			</article>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
